{"id":328571,"title":"结课测试｜这些容器技术的问题，你都掌握了么？","content":"<p>你好，我是程远。</p><p>《容器实战高手课》这门课程的必学内容已经全部结束了，感谢你一直以来的认真学习和支持！</p><p>我给你准备了一个结课小测试，希望可以帮助你检测一下这段时间的学习成果。</p><p>这套测试题共有 20 道题目，10道单选题，10道多选题，满分 100 分，系统自动评分。</p><p>还等什么，快点击下面按钮开始测试吧！</p><p><a href=\"http://time.geekbang.org/quiz/intro?act_id=357&exam_id=966\"><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/28/a4/28d1be62669b4f3cc01c36466bf811a4.png?wh=1142*201\" alt=\"\"></a></p><p>最后，这里有一份<a href=\"https://jinshuju.net/f/socZck\">毕业问卷</a>，题目不多，希望你可以花两分钟填一下。也十分期待能听到你的声音，说说你对这门课程的想法和建议。</p><!-- [[[read_end]]] -->","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":271786,"user_name":"百行吴书","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1806261,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3DFCBBEBCA9A4B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1b/8f/b5/7bc42adc.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1609809829,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14494711717","product_id":100063801,"comment_content":"果然不做笔记  只是在上下班的地铁上学一学的效率不高  刚好才60分","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":276122,"user_name":"徐少文","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1670331,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8E35B10DA44EE3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/7c/bb/635a2710.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1611800770,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"100265","content":"徐同学，谢谢你的留言。专栏专题的6讲，会从1月29日也就是明天更新哈，节奏还是每周一、三、五的时间。","user_name":"编辑回复","user_name_real":"赵宇新","uid":"1501385","ctime":1611812907,"ip_address":"","comment_id":276122,"utype":2}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5906768066","product_id":100063801,"comment_content":"老师后面的调试6讲什么时候上线啊，快等不及了","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1501385,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/e8/c9/59bcd490.jpg","nickname":"听水的湖","note":"","ucode":"B1759F90165D81","race_medal":0,"user_type":8,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"use